raw_data.name: Marketplace Coffee
raw_data.description: Good vibes. Relaxed atmosphere. We specialize in matcha and espresso

reviews_data.review_text: This place has amazing coffee! Amazing employee(s) as well!
Expresso was good! Owner was so nice. And I love how they use can lids for to go coffee. Very excited for this new coffee shop.
The cutest place with great coffee
Loved this new coffee shop in Mooresville, it’s a great atmosphere and the service was great. Drinks were delicious, can’t wait to visit again :)
Got some very delicious cold brew  and matcha with strawberry cold foam. Samantha is the owner and people were really excited to be there. She is cheery and the cold brew is excellent.

So happy I saw the corner sign for this CUTE coffee shop! It's located directly next door to Signature Jewelry. See photos for menu and hours. My iced vanilla latte with oat milk was delicious. Pebble ice ... need I say more?! They put their drinks in a can and then heat seal the top, so it's like drinking from a soda can. Very niche and a fun idea! This would be great when I'm riding bikes with my kids since I could throw my coffee in my bag and bring it with me instead of having to chug it before riding back home. I love that this cafe is here, and I can grab a coffee before running my errands in Morrison Plantation. Nothing against Starbucks, but I'd much rather support a local small business during my Harris Teeter grocery shopping. I'm excited to go back and try some of their food items!

Such a sweet little coffee shop! We love the coffee and cinnamon rolls. 🩷
And they have gluten free options!!!
So good. Iced caramel machiatto and a pumpkin muffin were just perfect and well priced. Only wish my large coffee was bigger.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you, may have to order an xl cup ;)

reviews_data.review_text:
Great prices, good food. Friendly and inviting vibe.

Been twice now, the marketplace breakfast was the perfect size for on the go morning.

Just saw this place opened and decided to try it out while I was in the area. It's a cute little hole-in-the-wall kind of shop. Got a yummy chai latte. While I didn't get food this time, I like that they mention that there are gluten-free options!

review_questions.Parking options: Free parking lot, Free street parking

reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you, hope you come back to try our food.

reviews_data.review_text: Brand new coffee shop in Mooresville! It has a quaint upscale vibe with fantastic options for every coffee lover. Give it a try!
The little coffee shop was SO cute and the owner (I presume) who was working was so sweet! Coffee was amazing and the avocado toast was even more amazing! 10/10 would recommend!
